Class Message

  • java.lang.Object
    • commonInfra.Message
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable

    public class Message
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable
    This data type defines the message sent between the server and the clients. The message is composed by a type and a set of parameters.
